          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 向日与你言辩一场，你怀恨在心，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（樵夫上，劝。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷子，三年前管的闲事，如今你老又管闲事。走罢，走罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李老丈作诈关儿。樵夫推李老丈同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿醒来。老娘在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓。岂不闻毋以远间亲，事亲者无失其为亲才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 今日里离间我娘儿，我娘儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，敢是你身体倦了？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（罗卜起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他对你讲些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他不曾讲些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既不曾讲些什么，为何闷倒在地？"
        },
        {
          "character": "罗卜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，老娘啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 孩儿见父之友，如见老父一般，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人言难足信，亲见始为真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘青提",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊罗卜儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孝顺歌） 哼儿吓，你且揾了泪，莫生疑，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（尾声） 儿今喜自夫来至，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘青提、罗卜同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
